The paper deals with content-based image retrieval, which is a problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The proposed method involves learning a similarity function, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also mentions the use of an objective function, which is a common concept in optimization (cs.AI).
